Package: CHESS.meadow.clustering
Title: Cluster Species + NEON AOP Spectra Into Map Training Samples
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ian", "Breckheimer", email = "ibreckhe@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Not a real package. This DESCRIPTION exists solely to drive renv
    dependency tracking for the CHESS_meadow_clustering analysis. The pipeline
    joins ESS-DIVE field vegetation data with NEON AOP spectra and clusters the
    combined feature space to seed training samples for a meadow map classifier.
